string.name: fileContent1
string.value: 1.Prepare a small pot and beat three eggs, add salt and sugar, beat with a whisk for seven or eight minutes, and add the cake powder to the egg batter twice.

string.name: fileContent2
string.value: 2.Pour corn oil into a bowl, add milk, beat the oil and milk with a whisk until completely integrated, and preheat the oven for 15 minutes.

string.name: fileContent3
string.value: 3.Prepare raisins, walnuts, paper cups, pour batter into paper cups, then add raisins and walnuts, and put cupcakes in the oven for 40 minutes.

string.name: fileContent4
string.value: 4.Prepare raisins, walnuts, paper cups, pour the batter into paper cups, then add raisins and walnuts, put cupcakes in the oven, time for 40 minutes, take out and serve.
